title: I am 108 lbs. Will 200 mg of propranolol at a time kill me? - Quora

response.answer_text: I have no intention of answering this with a definitive answer. if you are considering doing this, please reach out for the help you need and deserve. I edited the topics so that Quora’s list of places to get help appears. Please, look at that and call someone, or visit the websites. No matter how things look now, they will get better. Not as fast as you (and I) would like, but there will be better times for you.
